TITLE: Converting StatefulObservable to StatefulEvt in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This code demonstrates how to convert a StatefulObservable to a StatefulEvt using the statefulObservableToStatefulEvt utility function. It shows the basic implementation where you pass the StatefulObservable as a parameter, with an optional Context parameter.
SOURCE: https://github.com/keycloakify/keycloakify/blob/main/src/tools/StatefulObservable/README.md#2025-04-22_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import { statefulObservableToStatefulEvt } from "powerhooks/tools/StatefulObservable/statefulObservableToStatefulEvt";

const evtXyz = statefulObservableToStatefulEvt({
    statefulObservable: $xyz
    //Optionally you can pass a Ctx
});
```

