TITLE: Updated i18n Configuration TypeScript File
DESCRIPTION: Example of the source TypeScript file showing the new i18n configuration pattern using i18nBuilder
SOURCE: https://github.com/keycloakify/keycloakify/blob/main/stories/login/gpt.md#2025-04-22_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import { i18nBuilder } from "keycloakify/login/i18n";

const { useI18n, ofTypeI18n } = i18nBuilder
    .withThemeName<"my-theme-1" | "my-theme-2">()
    .withCustomTranslations({
        en: {
            myCustomMessage: "My custom message"
        },
        fr: {
            myCustomMessage: "Mon message personnalis√©"
        }
    })
    .build();

type I18n = typeof ofTypeI18n;

export { useI18n, type I18n };
```

